snippet.title: Monopoly: Build-a-Lot Edition - PC Gameplay
snippet.description:
An official collaboration between HipSoft, GameHouse and Hasbro in 2010.

The game does have a physical release, which is good, as being a licensed game means this is no longer available to purchase digitally from GameHouse.
